headline: Fox News Channel Finishes 2024 With Highest Audience Share in Nearly a Decade as It Marks Nine Years as Cable’s Most-Watched Network
summary: NEW YORK, January 02, 2025--FOX News Channel (FNC) continued to break ratings records in 2024, finishing the year with the highest share of the cable news audience in nearly a decade as it marks nine consecutive years as the highest-rated cable network in all of television, according to Nielsen Media Research.
